// iOS Google Maps SDK key, surfaced to the build as the MAPS_API_KEY build
// setting (referenced as $(MAPS_API_KEY) in Info.plist, read in AppDelegate).
//
// Locally this holds the key from wakey/.env. On Codemagic this file is
// REGENERATED in a pre-build step from the MAPS_API_KEY secret, so CI never
// relies on whatever is committed here.
//
// NOTE: enable "Maps SDK for iOS" in Google Cloud Console for this key, and
// ideally use an iOS-bundle-restricted key (com.wakey.wakey) rather than the
// Android one.
MAPS_API_KEY=AIzaSyAk9ZY0kuKnycZZkOU2bIL8tSZUkzqcSNM
